The paper discusses a framework that translates pre-trained ML pipelines into neural networks and fine-tunes the ML models within the pipeline jointly using backpropagation. This involves techniques related to machine learning, artificial intelligence, computer vision, natural language processing, and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
